name: The sixth incarnation. A monkey.
description:
After some time, I incarnated in a female monkey. The warm climate, a large amount of food, and a small flock population on a large island made life calm and measured. There were few predators and practically nothing threatened us.

We ate a lot of fruit, chewed the invigorating leaves of trees, frolicked a lot and multiplied. At some point, my life was reduced to an incessant cycle of childbirth. I gave birth to many offspring and nursed them.

Death overtook me unexpectedly. My vision failed. Thinking I was grabbing a branch, I grabbed a snake, which immediately bit me. The whole body became very painful and there was nothing to breathe. The pounding in my chest stopped. The soul left a completely worn-out spacesuit, which fully fulfilled its physiological function.
